og.description: Since coming to Grand Island in 2010, the Nebraska State Fair, at Fonner Park, has grown each year, offering the public a large diversity of entertainment, whether it is the many stage shows that are spread throughout the fairgrounds, the many strolling acts around the grounds, or the headline entertainers who take to the stage at the Heartland Event Center.
